---
title: Sweet Chili Chicken Breasts Sandwiches with Ranch and Side Salad
description: Wing-night flavours—in a sandwich! Sweet and sticky chili sauce smothers tender, golden chicken. You'll love the fresh side salad as a perfect hit of brightness, too!
